  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h3>We aim to provide each student at USP College with valuable industry placements. </h3>
<p>If you are interested in offering a placement please contact us using the details below. </p>
<p>After contacting us we’ll get in touch with you to discuss the process and go through the objectives. We will also provide full guidance on your responsibilities as an employer and the role of USP College as a facilitator.</p>
<p>We look forward to working with you to deliver outstanding industry placement learning to our young people.</p>]]></mainContent>
